King Goodwill Zwelithini has been blamed for sparking violence against foreigners in South Africa . 
  He said foreigners should 'pack their belongings' and 'leave the country' in a speech last month . 
  He has been accused of calling gay people 'rotten' and homosexuals 'lice' in the past . 
  King has also been criticised for lavish spending on his six wives and 28 children . 
  At least seven people have been killed in anti-immigrant violence in the last two weeks . 
  He was given 54million rand by the South African government . 
  He married his sixth wife in a lavish ceremony in July . 
 